The Telegraph - Calcutta
 Tuesday, June 17, 2003  Good Morning Hello It's Tuesday, June 17, 2003				 																Roads to avoid				 																																	Lower Circular Road, between Camac Street and Lansdowne Road, for the final phase of work on the AJC Bose Road flyover. Buses and minibuses from Beckbagan to Alipore zoo will take the Lansdowne Road-Elgin Road-Ashutosh Mukherjee RoadChowringhee-QueenswayHospital Road-Lower Circular Road route. Those travelling east towards Beckbagan will take the Ashutosh Mukherjee Road-Hazra Road-Ballygunge Phari-Syed Amir Ali Avenue route. 				 																Soiree				 																																	Rabindrasangeet and old Bengali songs by Iffat Ara Dewan at Sabhagar, Swabhumi, at 6.30 pm.				 																Meditation				 																																	A workshop on meditation, organised by Chinmaya Mission, at GD Birla Sabhagar, 7 pm to 8.30 pm.				 																Theatre				 																																	A theatre workshop for children at Aikatan, Salt Lake, from 10 am to 5 pm.				 																Season sale				 																																	The end-of-season sale of household accessories at Sasha, Mirza Ghalib Street, from 10 am to 7 pm.
